cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.HC, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the application of reinforcement learning methods to decision support systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new concept of non-deterministic policies, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The experiment with human subjects also suggests a connection to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
